<br>
A goofy, non-rp, or down right stupid name annoyes me, but as someone else pointed out some nicknames can seem a bit silly.<br>
<br>
Is there a reason for the name?  I'll roleplay with anyone but if they dont have a real good reason for it, Id probably suggest they change it or deny their application.  If someone cant take the time to think of a good name for their character... which is something that will float merrily above their head from now until deletion, what does that say about their dedication to other more fickle things, such as a guild? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~Vabris Vy'Tok, of House Vy'Tok~<br>
