<br>
I don't think I'd fault someone for running around with the name Poppy, Ankles, or Bill.  Since, after all, if you look around long enough, you'll find plenty of NPCs with similar names.  The idea of modern names vs. fantasy names is subjective to each and every person.  I wouldn't say Libbie is the most RPish of Gnome names, but I think it fits my character.  It's short, cute, and no nonsense. And heck, who knows where her parents came up with the name? <br>
<br>
After all, my RL parents gave me a name that is one of the most popular names for cats.  It's a family name.  *shrugs*<br>
